            <span class="utterance" who="tcharnabrodaR" start="1289.636" end="x">In the creamatories. And then—the creamtories were not yet completed. For that reason they gas-killed them in the bath house, and then they laid the bodies out in the field. There was a big ditch in the field, such as in a [word not clear] and there they were burned. For that reason we every week right after the selection, we observed a large square fire, and then we "felt" the smoke of burned flesh.</span>
