            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="tcharnabrodaR" start="2276.250" end="x">I was carried. The prisoners carried me, to Kirkheim. And from Kirkheim . . . I was completely sick, the legs were already black, so I was sent to the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>-<a class="term" href="#vothG_revier">revier</a>, <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> four, near <a class="placename" href="#vothL243">Landsberg</a>. The famous <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>-<a class="term" href="#vothG_revier">revier</a> in which thousands, more than thousands of people have died from spotted fever.</span>
        </li>
